metadata.name: Shades of Hope
metadata.created_by: The High Priestess and Her Lion
metadata.description:
The Source shines light on us exactly where it is needed and when it is needed. It may look dark, it may feel hazy, but it’s there. That’s the alignment along with Divine Timing which brings Manifestations into Reality.
